ygData.subject: Will help!
ygData.msgSnippet: If anyone has a character that they need help with, I d be glad to do that in my spare time. Just as long as you re on the Tunare server and I can reach yas
ygData.messageBody:
If anyone has a character that they need help
with, I'd be glad to do that in my spare time. Just as
long as you're on the Tunare server and I can reach
yas pretty easily. After all, being only of the 19th
means I can get to SOME places, but ah... I wouldn't
expect me to come help you fight in Nektulos or Grobb...
hehe. NOTE: I don't GIVE things away, not usually.
Buffs and Binds, yes. Teleports? ..Gonna have to wait
awhile before I get those. :) I will help with food
stuffs, spells, and hunting. But PLEASE don't think I'll
give up my Observer's just to help... I may be kind,
but kindness has it's limits, unfortunately... I
remember, a friend of mine donated 50pp to help out one of
his friend's characters. Needless to say, that
character wasn't seen again after that night... My friend
was pretty upset.<br><br> So... if your on the Tunare
server, look me up! Whether it be to ask for a possible
buff, bind, help with a SMALL quest, spells, etc. As
long as you ask nicely. I was helped out when I needed
it, it's time to repay the kindness. <br><br> See you
in Norrath!<br><br> ~Teppeny<br> Halfling Druid
(wannabe Bard) of the 19th<br> Souls of Peace<br> Tunare
